{
  "id": "RAW_bcf777",
  "title": "Gemini 2.5 的高级音频对话和生成能力",
  "url": "https://deepmind.google/discover/blog/advanced-audio-dialog-and-generation-with-gemini-25/",
  "date": "2025-06-03 16:00:01",
  "author": "Ankur Bapna",
  "siteName": "Google DeepMind Blog",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <uni-article-speakable style=\"height: 55px; margin-bottom: 36px; display: block;\" page-title=\"Advanced audio dialog and generation with Gemini 2.5\" listen-to-article=\"Listen to article\" data-date-modified=\"2025-06-03T16:00:01.852075+00:00\" data-tracking-ids=\"G-HGNBTNCHCQ,G-6NKTLKV14N\" data-voice-list=\"en.ioh-pngnat:Cyan,en.usb-pngnat:Lime\" data-script-src=\"https://www.gstatic.com/readaloud/player/web/api/js/api.js\">\n   <!---->\n   <div id=\"uni-article-speakable\">\n    <!--?lit$0704586605$--><span width=\"14px\">\n     <svg width=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 0 66 66\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"uni-spinner uni-spinner--small\">\n      <circle class=\"loader-path\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"7\" cx=\"33\" cy=\"33\" r=\"25\"></circle>\n     </svg></span>\n   </div>\n  </uni-article-speakable> <!--article text-->\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Advanced audio dialog and generation with Gemini 2.5&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"4ctxt\" class=\"drop-cap\">Gemini is built from the ground up to be multimodal, natively understanding and generating content across text, images, audio, video and code. At I/O we showed how Gemini 2.5 marks a significant step forward with new capabilities in AI-powered audio dialog and generation.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"drtva\">We’re already using these models to bring audio to users globally, across numerous products, prototypes and languages. <a href=\"https://blog.google/technology/google-labs/notebooklm-audio-overviews-50-languages/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://blog.google/technology/google-labs/notebooklm-audio-overviews-50-languages/&quot;}\">NotebookLM’s Audio Overviews</a> and <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/models/project-astra/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://deepmind.google/models/project-astra/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Project Astra</a> are just two examples. Here’s a closer look at what you can do with Gemini 2.5 native audio capabilities.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Advanced audio dialog and generation with Gemini 2.5&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"gp30l\">Real-time audio dialog</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"eg18s\">Human conversation is rich and nuanced, with meaning conveyed not just by <i>what</i> is said, but <i>how</i> it’s spoken — through tone, accent and even non-speech vocalizations, like laughter. We believe conversation will be a key way we interact with AI. That’s why Gemini reasons and generates speech natively in audio, enabling effective, real-time communication.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div><uni-youtube-player-article index=\"3\" thumbnail-alt=\"Multilingual capabilities\" video-id=\"9UmhcG7QS4c\" video-type=\"video\">\n   <!---->\n   <div data-yt-video=\"module\" class=\"article-video-special h-c-page--mobile-full-bleed \" data-analytics-module=\"{\n          &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Youtube Video&quot;,\n          &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;undefined&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"article-video-special__container\">\n     <div class=\"article-module uni-article-video uni-article-video--body\" data-component=\"uni-article-yt-player\" data-page-title=\"\" data-video-id=\"9UmhcG7QS4c\" data-index-id=\"3\" data-type=\"video\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n      <a role=\"video\" class=\"h-c-video h-c-video--marquee uni-article-video__custom-wrapper\" tabindex=\"0\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">\n       <div class=\"uni-article-video__aspect-image\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/9UmhcG7QS4c/default.webp\" alt=\"Multilingual capabilities\" data-loading=\"{\n                    &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;//i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/9UmhcG7QS4c/sddefault.webp&quot;,\n                    &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;//i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/9UmhcG7QS4c/mqdefault.webp&quot;\n                  }\"><uni-icon-component custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button--active\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" iconid=\"yt_video_play_button_no_hole\">\n         <!---->\n         <svg class=\"icon uni-article-video__play-button--active\" role=\"presentation\">\n          <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250528-1737#yt_video_play_button_no_hole\"></use>\n         </svg>\n        </uni-icon-component><uni-icon-component custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button\" custom-role=\"img\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" iconid=\"yt_video_play_button\" custom-label=\"Video Title \">\n         <!---->\n         <svg aria-label=\"Video Title \" class=\"icon uni-article-video__play-button\" role=\"img\">\n          <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250528-1737#yt_video_play_button\"></use>\n         </svg>\n        </uni-icon-component><!--?lit$0704586605$-->\n        <div class=\"uni-article-video__duration loading\">\n         <uni-icon-component iconid=\"yt_video_duration\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__duration-icon\" remove-viewbox=\"true\">\n          <!---->\n          <svg class=\"icon uni-article-video__duration-icon\" role=\"presentation\">\n           <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250528-1737#yt_video_duration\"></use>\n          </svg>\n         </uni-icon-component><span class=\"uni-article-video__duration-time\">00:00</span>\n        </div>\n       </div></a>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-youtube-player-article>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Advanced audio dialog and generation with Gemini 2.5&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"gp30l\">Native audio dialog with Gemini 2.5 Flash preview features:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"4um9m\"><b>Natural conversation:</b> Voice interactions of remarkable quality, more appropriate expressivity, and prosody (patterns of rhythm), delivered with very low latency so you can converse fluidly.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"5k52d\"><b>Style control:</b> Using natural language prompts, you can adapt the delivery within the conversation, steering it to adopt specific accents, produce a range of tones and expressions and even whisper.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"6500o\"><b>Tool integration:</b> Gemini 2.5 can use tools and function calling during dialog. This allows it to incorporate real-time information from sources like Google Search or use custom developer-built tools, making conversations more practical.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"ee1rr\"><b>Conversation context awareness (proactive audio):</b> Our system is trained to discern and disregard background speech, ambient conversations and other irrelevant audio, responding when appropriate. Basically, it understands when <i>not</i> to speak.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"1burv\"><b>Audio-video understanding:</b> With native support from streaming audio and video, Gemini 2.5 can converse with you about what it sees in a video feed or through screen sharing.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"2ghe7\"><b>Multilinguality:</b> Converse in any of our 24+ <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/speech-generation#languages\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/speech-generation#languages&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">supported languages</a>, or even easily mix languages within the same phrase.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"14gha\"><b>Affective dialog:</b> Gemini 2.5 responds to the user's tone of voice, recognizing that the same words spoken differently can lead to very different conversations.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"74ddo\"><b>Advanced thinking dialog:</b> Gemini’s reasoning capabilities can enhance its conversation, leading to overall better performance across all features. This leads to more coherent and intelligent interactions, particularly for complex reasoning tasks.</li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Advanced audio dialog and generation with Gemini 2.5&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"gp30l\">Controllable text-to-speech (TTS)</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"2eift\">The evolution of text-to-speech technology is moving rapidly, and with our latest models, we're moving beyond naturalness to giving unprecedented control over generated audio. Now you can generate anything from short snippets to long-form narratives, precisely dictating style, tone, emotional expression and performance — all steerable through natural language prompts.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div><uni-youtube-player-article index=\"6\" thumbnail-alt=\"Text to speech demo\" video-id=\"zwb4cTtRNIo\" video-type=\"video\">\n   <!---->\n   <div data-yt-video=\"module\" class=\"article-video-special h-c-page--mobile-full-bleed \" data-analytics-module=\"{\n          &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Youtube Video&quot;,\n          &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;undefined&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"article-video-special__container\">\n     <div class=\"article-module uni-article-video uni-article-video--body\" data-component=\"uni-article-yt-player\" data-page-title=\"\" data-video-id=\"zwb4cTtRNIo\" data-index-id=\"6\" data-type=\"video\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n      <a role=\"video\" class=\"h-c-video h-c-video--marquee uni-article-video__custom-wrapper\" tabindex=\"0\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">\n       <div class=\"uni-article-video__aspect-image\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/zwb4cTtRNIo/default.webp\" alt=\"Text to speech demo\" data-loading=\"{\n                    &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;//i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/zwb4cTtRNIo/sddefault.webp&quot;,\n                    &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;//i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/zwb4cTtRNIo/mqdefault.webp&quot;\n                  }\"><uni-icon-component custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button--active\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" iconid=\"yt_video_play_button_no_hole\">\n         <!---->\n         <svg class=\"icon uni-article-video__play-button--active\" role=\"presentation\">\n          <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250528-1737#yt_video_play_button_no_hole\"></use>\n         </svg>\n        </uni-icon-component><uni-icon-component custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button\" custom-role=\"img\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" iconid=\"yt_video_play_button\" custom-label=\"Video Title \">\n         <!---->\n         <svg aria-label=\"Video Title \" class=\"icon uni-article-video__play-button\" role=\"img\">\n          <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250528-1737#yt_video_play_button\"></use>\n         </svg>\n        </uni-icon-component><!--?lit$0704586605$-->\n        <div class=\"uni-article-video__duration loading\">\n         <uni-icon-component iconid=\"yt_video_duration\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__duration-icon\" remove-viewbox=\"true\">\n          <!---->\n          <svg class=\"icon uni-article-video__duration-icon\" role=\"presentation\">\n           <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250528-1737#yt_video_duration\"></use>\n          </svg>\n         </uni-icon-component><span class=\"uni-article-video__duration-time\">00:00</span>\n        </div>\n       </div></a>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-youtube-player-article> <uni-youtube-player-article index=\"7\" thumbnail-alt=\"Multi speaker text to speech demo\" video-id=\"k7uU-XjDpOo\" video-type=\"video\">\n   <!---->\n   <div data-yt-video=\"module\" class=\"article-video-special h-c-page--mobile-full-bleed \" data-analytics-module=\"{\n          &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Youtube Video&quot;,\n          &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;undefined&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"article-video-special__container\">\n     <div class=\"article-module uni-article-video uni-article-video--body\" data-component=\"uni-article-yt-player\" data-page-title=\"\" data-video-id=\"k7uU-XjDpOo\" data-index-id=\"7\" data-type=\"video\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n      <a role=\"video\" class=\"h-c-video h-c-video--marquee uni-article-video__custom-wrapper\" tabindex=\"0\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">\n       <div class=\"uni-article-video__aspect-image\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/k7uU-XjDpOo/default.webp\" alt=\"Multi speaker text to speech demo\" data-loading=\"{\n                    &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;//i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/k7uU-XjDpOo/sddefault.webp&quot;,\n                    &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;//i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/k7uU-XjDpOo/mqdefault.webp&quot;\n                  }\"><uni-icon-component custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button--active\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" iconid=\"yt_video_play_button_no_hole\">\n         <!---->\n         <svg class=\"icon uni-article-video__play-button--active\" role=\"presentation\">\n          <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250528-1737#yt_video_play_button_no_hole\"></use>\n         </svg>\n        </uni-icon-component><uni-icon-component custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button\" custom-role=\"img\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" iconid=\"yt_video_play_button\" custom-label=\"Video Title \">\n         <!---->\n         <svg aria-label=\"Video Title \" class=\"icon uni-article-video__play-button\" role=\"img\">\n          <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250528-1737#yt_video_play_button\"></use>\n         </svg>\n        </uni-icon-component><!--?lit$0704586605$-->\n        <div class=\"uni-article-video__duration loading\">\n         <uni-icon-component iconid=\"yt_video_duration\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__duration-icon\" remove-viewbox=\"true\">\n          <!---->\n          <svg class=\"icon uni-article-video__duration-icon\" role=\"presentation\">\n           <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250528-1737#yt_video_duration\"></use>\n          </svg>\n         </uni-icon-component><span class=\"uni-article-video__duration-time\">00:00</span>\n        </div>\n       </div></a>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-youtube-player-article>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Advanced audio dialog and generation with Gemini 2.5&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"gp30l\">Additional controls and capabilities include:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"61qj7\"><b>Dynamic performance:</b> These models can bring text to life for expressive readings for anything from poetry to newscasts to engaging storytelling. They can also perform with specific emotions and produce accents when requested.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"d25ej\"><b>Enhanced pace and pronunciation control:</b> Control delivery speed and ensure more accuracy in pronunciation, including for specific words.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"gq4h\"><b>Multi-speaker dialogue generation:</b> This model can generate two-person “<a href=\"https://blog.google/technology/ai/notebooklm-audio-overviews/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://blog.google/technology/ai/notebooklm-audio-overviews/&quot;}\">NotebookLM-style</a>” audio overview from text input, making content more engaging through conversation.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"7tit\"><b>Multilinguality:</b> Create multilingual audio content effortlessly with Gemini 2.5, offering the same support for more than 24 <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/speech-generation#languages\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/speech-generation#languages&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">languages</a>.</li>\n     </ul>\n     <p data-block-key=\"6vgae\">For controllable speech generation (TTS), choose Gemini 2.5 Pro Preview for state-of-the-art quality on complex prompts, or Gemini 2.5 Flash Preview for cost-efficient everyday applications. This allows developers to dynamically create audio for announcements, stories, podcasts, video games and more.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Advanced audio dialog and generation with Gemini 2.5&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-compononent-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"gp30l\">Safety and responsibility</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"433dq\">We’ve proactively assessed potential risks throughout every stage of the development process for these native audio features, using what we’ve learned to inform our mitigation strategies. We validate these measures through rigorous internal and external safety evaluations, including comprehensive <a href=\"https://blog.google/technology/safety-security/googles-ai-red-team-the-ethical-hackers-making-ai-safer/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://blog.google/technology/safety-security/googles-ai-red-team-the-ethical-hackers-making-ai-safer/&quot;}\">red teaming</a> for responsible deployment. Additionally, all audio outputs from our models are embedded with <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/science/synthid\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://deepmind.google/science/synthid&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">SynthID</a>, our watermarking technology, to ensure transparency by making AI-generated audio identifiable.</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"d2e3i\">Native audio capabilities for developers</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"fk474\">We’re bringing native audio outputs to Gemini 2.5 models, giving developers new capabilities to build richer, more interactive applications via the Gemini API in <a href=\"http://aistudio.google.com/\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;http://aistudio.google.com/&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google AI Studio</a> or <a href=\"https://console.cloud.google.com/freetrial?redirectPath=/vertex-ai/studio\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://console.cloud.google.com/freetrial?redirectPath=/vertex-ai/studio&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Vertex AI</a>.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"epk97\">To begin exploring, developers can try native audio dialog with Gemini 2.5 Flash preview in Google AI Studio’s <a href=\"https://aistudio.google.com/live\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;https://aistudio.google.com/live&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">stream</a> tab. Controllable speech generation (TTS) is available in preview for both Gemini 2.5 Pro and Flash by selecting speech generation in the <a href=\"http://aistudio.google.com/generate-speech\" data-analytics-onclick=\"{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;page interaction&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;in-article links&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;link click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;http://aistudio.google.com/generate-speech&quot;}\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">generate media</a> tab within Google AI Studio.<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Gemini 2.5 引入了先进的原生音频对话和可控生成能力。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Gemini 2.5 引入了先进的原生音频对话和可控生成能力。",
  "summary": "这篇来自 Google DeepMind 的文章详细介绍了多模态 Gemini 2.5 模型中的全新原生音频功能。文章重点强调了实时音频对话方面的重大进展，实现了自然、上下文感知和风格可控的对话。其关键功能涵盖低延迟、通过自然语言提示调整语音风格、工具集成、背景噪音识别、音视频理解、多语言能力以及情感对话。此外，模型提供了可控的文本转语音（TTS）功能，支持动态表现、语速/发音控制以及多说话人生成能力。文章强调了 SynthID 水印等安全措施，并指出这些能力已通过 Google AI Studio 和 Vertex AI 中的 Gemini API 向开发者开放，为更丰富、更具交互性的 AI 应用开启了新的可能性。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Gemini 2.5 支持原生多模态音频能力。",
      "explanation": "这些模型旨在理解和生成跨模态内容，包括将音频与文本、图像、视频和代码深度集成。"
    },
    {
      "point": "实时音频对话自然且可控。",
      "explanation": "低延迟、通过提示控制风格、工具集成和上下文感知等功能使 AI 对话更加流畅、富有表现力和实用。"
    },
    {
      "point": "文本转语音提供对输出的细粒度控制。",
      "explanation": "用户可以指定风格、语气、情感，甚至生成多说话人对话，从基本的自然度提升到动态表现。"
    },
    {
      "point": "集成了 SynthID 等安全措施。",
      "explanation": "主动风险评估、红队测试和水印等措施确保了 AI 生成音频输出的负责任部署和透明度。"
    },
    {
      "point": "新的音频功能可供开发者使用。",
      "explanation": "通过 Google AI Studio 和 Vertex AI 的可用性使开发者能够利用这些先进能力构建创新、交互式应用。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Gemini 从零开始构建，旨在成为多模态模型，原生理解和生成跨文本、图像、音频、视频和代码的内容。",
    "我们相信对话将是与 AI 互动的一种关键方式。这就是 Gemini 原生具备在音频中进行推理和生成语音能力的原因，从而实现有效的实时沟通。",
    "使用自然语言提示，你可以在对话中调整声音表现，使其采用特定口音，产生各种语气和表情，甚至耳语。",
    "现在你可以生成从短片段到长篇叙述的任何内容，精确指定风格、语气、情感表达和表现——所有这些都可以通过自然语言提示进行控制。",
    "此外，我们模型的所有音频输出都嵌入了我们的水印技术 SynthID，通过使 AI 生成的音频可识别来确保透明度。"
